desc: Roots to Fruits Nursery in Southwestern Wisconsin. Online, seasonal retail locations near Soldiers Grove. Retail and wholesale heirloom and modern disease resistant apple and other fruit trees, nut trees, berry plants, grape vines, landscape trees, ornamentals, garden supplies. Orchard services, planning to pruning.

layout.text: Roots to Fruits now carries a full line of vines for grape growers of all levels.
